 higher level, with equal playtime. The relative difference will shrink post-65, but because the halfling started earning AAs earlier, he'll have more. Combined with hide and no size or faction issues that makes halflings a pretty good bet. No way is frontal stun immunity worth 15% of your *total* exp, especially now that AAs exist to make that up.<br>
<br>
Of course, these are all really distinctions without a difference, and you should just play whatever graphic you feel like looking at the most. I enjoy my ogre, and don't regret him -- sometimes it's nice to be huge. Ogres do easily become the centers of raids.<br>
<br>
