has been talked about.<br>
<br>
The fact that some races can use Rallos cultural (fierce heraldic) and Tribunal cultural (helanic tundra) helps them in the gear race for a while. This is probably more significant than the actual race you choose. Dunno who can wear Zekkoid stuff, but barbs, humans and half elfs can wear helanic tundra. This stuff is better than most stuff you'll see until you get into the Ssra range.<br>
